IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User thejefflarson@gmail.com
PassCmd "getpasswd imap.google.com thejefflarson@gmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile ~/.certs
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]/Spam
Create Both
Expunge Both
Remove Both
SyncState *

